The Dropbox security team is responsible for securing data at a massive scale. Over half a billion users and 300,000 teams trust us to keep their private data safe. To be worthy of this trust, we have a well staffed security team of hardworking and passionate individuals. If you are looking to join a strong and growing team with interesting, high-impact and multifaceted work, this could be the right fit for you.

Interns will join edX as a member of a “squad” dedicated to one of edX’s key business initiatives, whether its product or platform-based. These squads complete work that’s crucial to edX’s product roadmap and success! There will be opportunities to collaborate with folks within your own team, with other interns, and with key stakeholders across the organization.

event_information: Interns at Strava are considered full members of the engineering team.They build software that gets deployed to millions of athletes. We’ll give you experienced mentors and all the tools you need to make a meaningful impact on our product.

As a Product Analyst Intern you will be a key member of our cross functional product teams. You will work closely with product managers, designers, engineers, researchers and product marketers to drive tactical and strategic decision-making with data. The successful candidate will have a passion for data, a deep curiosity to find impactful insights, and a desire to community results to impact the business. This position is a 3-month summer internship position on our Analytics team.

Making a positive impact on society, gaining hands-on consulting experience, and networking with Accenture leaders are just a few of the perks of the Accenture Innovation Challenge. Bring your most creative ideas to life by helping our nonprofit client solve a real-life business problem.

event_title: ICG Technology, Summer Software Development Analyst
event_information: We’re committed to teaching you the ropes. The Summer Analyst Program starts in early July with an in-depth education on the fundamentals of the Analyst role, as well as the nuances of Citi’s culture. The program also includes on the desk training, an informative speaker series as well as networking opportunities. Summer Analysts often return to Citi after graduating from University to become full-time Analysts and continue their career in technology.

We’re looking for Software Engineers to join the Yext Engineering team and drive the technology behind our revolutionary product offering! Our team works in an agile environment running two-week sprints that culminate with demos of features in progress. You will work alongside engineers from the top universities and tech companies in the world, hands-on with the code from day one.

As a Full Stack Developer, you will be working with our internal Professional Services team, clients, and third-party teams to plan, architect, develop, and extend custom client products. We expect that you have 2-5 years of experience and an excellent background in Java. Additionally, you should have experience and familiarity with Javascript, MySQL, Spring web application, third party integrations, APIs, and Apache web configuration. We are an incredibly supportive group, and we crave new, challenging ideas.

Applied Machine Learning Research at Netflix is aimed at improving various aspects of our business, including personalization algorithms, systems optimization, content valuation, and streaming video optimization. As such, our research spans many Machine Learning areas, including recommender systems, causal inference, reinforcement learning, computer vision, natural language processing, optimization and operations research.
The Guardian Software Engineering Fellowship is an opportunity for developers who are at the beginning of their careers to join our Product and Engineering department.

The Splice Engineering Team builds and maintains customer facing software with a shared architecture direction and delightful developer experience.  We have teams that focus on Quality, SRE, Platform Engineering, as well as teams that focus on customer facing features and functionality.
